OL,7,FChloe Keedy reports on the thousands
OL,8,Fof women who could now receive
OL,9,Fcompensation following the sodium
OL,10,Fvalproate and pelvic mesh scandals.
OL,12,FWords by Will Tullis
OL,14,FThousands of women and children
OL,15,Faffected by two separate medical
OL,16,Fscandals - one involving the epilepsy
OL,17,Fmedication sodium valproate, and
OL,18,Fanother involving vaginal mesh used to
OL,19,Ftreat prolapses - have a "clear case"
OL,20,Ffor compensation, a new report has
OL,21,Fsaid.
