OL,3,CVictims of sodium valproate and mesh
OL,4,Cimplant scandals should get
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe review by England's Patient Safety
OL,8,FCommissioner highlights how thousands
OL,9,Fof women's lives were "destroyed" due
OL,10,Fto pelvic mesh, and thousands of
OL,11,Fchildren "will never be able to live
OL,12,Findependent lives" after being exposed
OL,13,Fto sodium valproate.
OL,15,FEpilepsy treatment sodium valproate
OL,16,Fhas been linked to physical
OL,17,Fmalformations, autism and
OL,18,Fdevelopmental delay in some children
OL,19,Fwhen it is taken by their mothers
OL,20,Fwhile pregnant.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/11
