OL,4,Cimplant scandals should get
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FVaginal mesh implants have been used
OL,8,Fto treat urinary and gynaecological
OL,9,Fconditions, but have caused
OL,10,Fdebilitating harm to some women.
OL,12,FThe report says there is a "clear
OL,13,Fcase" for redress based on the
OL,14,F"systemic" healthcare and regulatory
OL,15,Ffailures for women and children
OL,16,Faffected by the issues in England.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/11
