OL,7,F"My report could not be clearer ` the
OL,8,Fcase for redress has been made," Dr
OL,9,FHughes said.
OL,11,F"It highlights in detail the daily
OL,12,Fproblems that impact on those who have
OL,13,Fbeen harmed, who have seen their lives
OL,14,Fdestroyed by pelvic mesh, and the
OL,15,Fchildren who will never be able to
OL,16,Flive independent lives," she added.
