OL,3,CVictims of sodium valproate and mesh
OL,4,Cimplant scandals should get
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FEmma Friedmann has epilepsy and had
OL,8,Fbeen told by her neurologist there was
OL,9,F"minimal" risk of taking sodium
OL,10,Fvalproate. Her son Andy, now 25, was
OL,11,Fthen born with foetal valproate
OL,12,Fsyndrome. Andy has dyspraxia and
OL,13,Fautism and needs full-time care.
OL,15,F"I feel guilty for having epilepsy, I
OL,16,Ffeel guilty for taking the drug, I
OL,17,Ffeel guilty for trusting my
OL,18,Fneurologist," Emma told ITV News after
OL,19,Fattending an event in Parliament for
OL,20,Fthe report's publication.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/11
