OL,7,F"We have to get this fixed we are a
OL,8,Fdeveloped nation, we should not be
OL,9,Fleaving these families to suffer,"
OL,10,FEmma said.
OL,12,F"I feel reassured that these things
OL,13,Fhave come out in the open," she added.
