OL,4,Cimplant scandals should get
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FEngland's Patient Safety Commissioner,
OL,8,FDr Henrietta Hughes, wanted to include
OL,9,Fpatients that had suffered avoidable
OL,10,Fharm as a result of hormone pregnancy
OL,11,Ftests, including Primodos, in her
OL,12,Freview but was told by the Department
OL,13,Fof Health and Social Care (DHSC) they
OL,14,Fwould not be included.
OL,16,FMarie Lyon, chairwoman of the
OL,17,FAssociation For Children Damaged by
OL,18,FHormone Pregnancy Tests, said that
OL,19,Ffamilies who took hormone pregnancy
OL,20,Ftests between 1958 and 1978 felt
OL,21,F"betrayed".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/11
