OL,7,FShe said many were never told of the
OL,8,Frisks of Primodos and were instructed
OL,9,Fto take the drug ` which is 40 times
OL,10,Fthe strength of an oral contraceptive
OL,11,Fpill ` by their GPs as a way of
OL,12,Ffinding out whether or not they were
OL,13,Fpregnant.
OL,15,FHormone pregnancy tests were withdrawn
OL,16,Ffrom the market in the late 1970s and
OL,17,Fmanufacturers have faced claims that
OL,18,Fsuch tests led to a number of adverse
OL,19,Foutcomes including birth defects and
OL,20,Fmiscarriages.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/11
