OL,7,FMs Lyon, 77, said that families feel
OL,8,Fas though they have been "left out in
OL,9,Fthe cold".
OL,11,F"I feel betrayed by the Patient Safety
OL,12,FCommissioner, by the IMMDS review
OL,13,F(Independent Medicines and Medical
OL,14,FDevices Safety Review) and by the
OL,15,Fsecretary of state for Health ` all
OL,16,Fthree have betrayed our families
OL,17,Fbecause basically they have just
OL,18,Fforgotten us," Ms Lyon said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/11
