OL,7,F"It's a case of 'it's too difficult so
OL,8,Fwe will just focus on valproate and
OL,9,Fmesh'."
OL,11,FIn response to the report, Women's
OL,12,Fhealth minister, Maria Caulfield MP
OL,13,Fsaid the government is "focused" on
OL,14,Fimproving how the system listens to
OL,15,Fpatients and healthcare professionals
OL,16,Fand introducing measures to make
OL,17,Fmedicines and devices safer.
